# CLIP ChangeLog for x11-apps/arandr

*arandr-0.1.9 (25 Oct 2017)

  25 Oct 2017; Nicolas Godinho <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +arandr-0.1.9.ebuild, -arandr-0.1.7.1.ebuild:
  Bump to latest stable to support more recent xrandr version.

*arandr-0.1.7 (04 Nov 2014)

  04 Nov 2014; Tony Cheneau <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +arandr-0.1.7.ebuild, -arandr-0.1.6-r2.ebuild:
  Bump to arandr-0.1.7 in order to parse more recent xrandr version.
  Reintroduce the configuration save/load feature (more secure file selection).
  Add standalone tool to load configurations.

*arandr-0.1.6-r2 (08 Aug 2013)

  08 Aug 2013; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +arandr-0.1.6-r2.ebuild, -arandr-0.1.6-r1.ebuild:
  Bump to fix shebang. Switch to distutils-r1 while we're at it.

*arandr-0.1.6-r1 (24 Jul 2013)

  24 Jul 2013; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +arandr-0.1.6-r1.ebuild, -arandr-0.1.6.ebuild:
  Force rebuild - newer python.

*arandr-0.1.6 (08 Feb 2013)

  08 Feb 2013; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +arandr-0.1.6.ebuild, -arandr-0.1.5.ebuild,
  -files/arandr-0.1.3-clip.patch, -files/arandr-0.1.5-fr.patch, 
  +files/arandr-0.1.6-clip.patch:
  Bump to latest. Smallish localization + UI streamlining - remove
  useless menus, do not display screens which are not connected.
  Merge french localization fix patch into clip patch.
  Quick & dirty hack to display 'LCD' instead of 'LVDS'.

*arandr-0.1.5 (23 Mar 2012)

  23 Mar 2012; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +arandr-0.1.5.ebuild, -arandr-0.1.4-r1.ebuild,
  -files/arandr-0.1.4-fr.patch, +files/arandr-0.1.5-fr.patch:
  Bump to latest.

*arandr-0.1.4-r1 (03 Aug 2011)

  03 Aug 2011; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +arandr-0.1.4-r1.ebuild, -arandr-0.1.4.ebuild,
  +files/arandr-0.1.4-fr.patch, -files/arandr-0.1.3-fr.patch:
  Remove useless localization patch (fr.po is now included in 
  the upstream tarball, patch got applied ok but with the wrong
  -pN level ...). Add a smallish localization fix patch instead.

*arandr-0.1.4 (12 Jul 2011)

  12 Jul 2011; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +arandr-0.1.4.ebuild, -arandr-0.1.3.ebuild,
  +files/arandr-0.1.4-xrandr-parse.patch:
  Bump to latest and add a patch to not crash when xrandr returns
  modes like '1024x768i' (note trailing 'i').
  Grrr, had to do regexps in python...

*arandr-0.1.3 (24 Mar 2010)

  24 Mar 2010; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  Initial import, based on gentoo bug #231669. Bumped, added
  missing depends, patched in French translations.
